folder: Metropolitan Ave & at intersection of Cooper Ave, Queens, NY
text:
Metropolitan Ave., south side, at its intersection with Cooper Ave. showing the Saflian Jaeger farmhouse and outbuildings. Some of the owners were:Jaflian Jaeger 1873, G. Yeager 1891, L. Whitemeyer 1896, and one Berkaeyer in 1909. A gas station occupied its site in 1929. This is a
set of two views.
April 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
(3)  Another and more distant view of the house, seen from
Woodhaven Bodlevard.
Eugene L. Armbruster Cotiection
April, 1923
title: Queens: Metropolitan Ave - at intersection of Cooper Ave
